ing efforts have been shut down by VA supreme court. All these past decades the democrats has had an unfair advantage because the voting rights act allowed for white people to be discriminated against. If we pass the SAVE act then America might actually be saved and we can start making progress instead of regaining lost ground. Have a good Mother\u2019s Day weekend everyone. Be safe.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 32, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2052581402810458357", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsL9qViz", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 34, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8607181, "raw_content": "", "author": "mohel", "created": 1778265096032, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Tulkas71", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsL9qViz.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/LightOnLiberty/status/2052581402810458357", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "California's online voter registration system operates on an \"honor system\" where literally anyone in the world can register to vote by simply clicking a box saying they're not lying. No verification, no citizenship checks. Just click and you're registered.", "last_comment_created": 1778271030335, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up":